She tilted her head a bit "Ah I see....."

Venor is silent for a bit, then unstrings her bow, putting her arrow back in the quiver and the bow over her shoulder before simply.... unwrapping her legs and falling to the ground, flipping upright as she does so. She lands casually, bending her knees to absorb the impact.
Her tails wagged a small bit "So....What brings you back to the forest?" She tilted her head

"I guess I needed a break. I have... a family, a friend... a revolution to win, and emotions to regain. I don't feel any stress but my family insisted I take a break." Venor closes all but her main eyes.
".....Theres.....a revolution....? Against who????" She tilted her head to the other side. Did she really not know about the plasma?

Her tails fluffed up and she went into her mun form hoping it would look less threatening "What????? No???? I hardly ever leave the forest...and not many people come here. I only was given missions by a kind of messenger bird....which....hasnt come in a while...."

Her lips curl, displaying her sharp teeth and letting dark smoke waft out. Hypnotism. "You will tell me whether you are lying or not." she speaks clearly, stirring up her smoke as she does - She's confident in her hypnotism abilities.
"I am not lying." She said, staring at the other. Due to her mask being on, Venor couldn't see the semi annoyed look on her face.

Venor lowers her bow and Careless Whisper returns to Evolution 2, it's fox form. Venor doesn't close her eyes, though, but she breathes out and the smoke dissipates. In an instant, its back over her shoulder. "Would you like me to catch you up?"
"Yes please, That would be nice..." She adjusted her mask a small bit "...Do you like tea?? We can talk over tea if you want.."

Venor closes her main eyes for a second, giving the impression she doesn't have any. "Sure." She gnaws her lip, eyes darting over the direction where her cave is, but only the back ones. The rest remain fixed on Vulpe and the landscape.
She went into her kitsune form again. "Alright well its this way..." She began to walk

"Kitsune?" Venor asks, and puts her hand on the ground. Careless Whisper flops onto her arm and she carries her stand to her shoulder.
"Basically a 9 tailed fox. A type of Yokai." She hummed, going back into her mun form and going to make some tea
